node.text:
NEW COFFEE ALERT!! There’s seriously nothing better than a fresh cup of coffee in the morning! (Ad)  @FourSigmatic  just launched into select Target stores across California and are available to purchase online for door delivery nationwide! 
Four Sigmatic elevates fair trade, single origin Arabica coffee from Honduras with functional mushrooms and adaptogens. My favorite is the Think Coffee with Lion's Mane mushroom to support productivity and creativity. It tastes like coffee not like mushrooms. No jitters, just hours of crash-free focus. Make sure to add @FourSigmatic on your next target.com order or pickup at select CA @Target stores near you 🎯

|ad| Calm + Restore your skin’s barrier with  @aveenous now available @target. I’ve been using Aveeno’s Calm + Restore Nourishing Oat Cleanser and Oat Gel Moisturizer for the last few months and my skin feels so hydrated and nourished now. If your skin needs a boost, then this line is a great way to start. Especially if you have sensitive skin like me.

•Key Ingredients: Feverfew (calms skin) & Nourishing Oat (soothes skin)

•Formulated without fragrance, parabens, sulfates, and phthalates
